description:
Apply Today!  
https://fountainviewacademy.ca/fountainview-apply/

Are you ready for an amazing High School experience? Discover Fountainview Academy. 

We offer an inspiring music program, an accredited academic program, leadership training, a successful vocational program, and the opportunity for spiritual growth by witnessing through media and more, all guided by the principles of true education. 

Our campus is in the country, among the rugged coastal mountains of beautiful British Columbia, Canada. Experience our amazing program for yourself!

===

If you enjoyed this video, dont forget to subscribe and enable notifications for our channel so you never miss an upload!

Check out https://www.fountainview.tv/ for an ad-free listening experience and exclusive content!

Connect with us by sending in prayer requests, asking a Bible question, or signing up for free Bible Studies! Click the link to find out more: https://faconnect.ca/

===

 Subscribe for new videos: https://bit.ly/2QMi67G

 Buy our other sheet music, devotionals, and DVD: http://store.fountainview.ca/ 

 Spotify Music: https://spoti.fi/39fv32U

 Amazon Music: http://bit.ly/2vaey9J

 Apple Music: https://apple.co/2UwuZaK

===

Follow us!

 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fountainviewacademy

 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fountainviewacademy

 Fountainview Live Streams: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC05RinrBWDfnPwVHvoEwttQ/

===

Fountainview Academy is a Christian high school based in southern British Columbia, Canada, which holds Province of BC Ministry of Education accreditation. Students from all over the world are attracted to Fountainview because of its balanced approach to education. Each staff member is personally committed to the eternal success of every student, and together they strive for the highest standards in every respect. If you're interested in attending Fountainview Academy, click here to learn more: https://fountainviewacademy.ca/admissions/apply/
